flowchart TD
    A([Raw training data]) --> B[Data validation and quality checks]
    B --> C{Data quality pass?}
    C -- Fail --> D([Alert: data quality issue])
    C -- Pass --> E[Train / validation / test split]
    E --> F[Feature scaling and encoding]
    F --> G[Model training on train split]
    G --> H{Hyperparameter tuning?}
    H -- Yes --> I[Launch parallel tuning runs]
    I --> J[Select best checkpoint from validation metrics]
    H -- No --> J
    J --> K[Evaluate on held-out test set]
    K --> L{Metrics above threshold?}
    L -- Fail --> M([Fail pipeline: trigger review])
    L -- Pass --> N[Package model artifact with metadata]
    N --> O[Register in model registry]
    O --> P([Trigger deployment pipeline])
